high_descs: Walk to the night stand to the right of the bed and look down.
Pick up the alarm clock on the night stand and look up.
With the alarm clock, turn around and walk straight to the desk against the wall.
Place the alarm clock between the keys and cup on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Place an alarm clock on the desk.

high_descs: Turn right and walk all the way around the night stand on the opposite side of the bed
Pick up the alarm clock from the night stand
Turn around and walk forward to the shelf
Put the alarm clock on top of the shelf
anns.task_desc: Put the alarm clock on top of the shelf

high_descs: Turn right, walk a few steps, turn left, walk to the wall, then turn left and walk up to the nightstand.
Pick up the alarm clock that is on the nightstand.
Turn around completely, walk to the end of the bed, turn right, then turn left and walk up to the table.
Place the alarm clock down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move an alarm clock to the table.
